Reason for being in the climb section is basically its just climb.

This is only a level that I can change the size of or change the layout of.

This is a preview and is in **ALPHA**!

Things are subject to change.

Things that will change:
- That big button (might become a detection to whoever lands on the platform)
- The rotated block
- Adding a hub
- Button telling who won (If anybody knows how please explain in the comments or link a link to a tutorial)
- More climb maps
- Removing weapons on spawn

Things that might change:

- Jump Sizes
- Difficulty
- Map name

Things that wont change:

- Currently none

Feedback Appreciated!

Installing is simple and easy!

1. Open the RAR with a compatible program. (winrar, winzip, etc.)

2. Copy the .bsp file included in the RAR file to C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps

3. Click create server and find the map OR open console and type map MG_ClimbingWars and it should show up then click on it and hit enter.

P.S.

I am too lazy to delete the area I started with currently so you can just noclip to the area of the level I used to test a few things. (Will be deleted next preview)
